{
  "texts": [
    "These models range in computational complexity, profundity, and the number of features they can represent.",
    "Despite this, the use of a single, pre-trained model may not be adequate to account for all the features that are present in medical imagery.",
    "Multi-CNNs work better by combining several models that have already been trained.",
    "This improves the accuracy of classifying medical images by using the best features from each model for feature extraction.",
    "This integration is particularly advantageous in medical imaging, which requires a precise and accurate evaluation of the patient's condition."
  ]
}